name: Shard Life Drawing Series No 1 of 8
description: This is the first collectable in a series of eight drawings. Drawn in a life drawn session from a 10 minute pose in my signature "shard" style and offered free for you to start collecting. 128 copies are minted. The following collectables in this series will be minted 2^(8-n) copies at 2^(n-1) tez each. See Instagram (@nulnul7) for more works in this style.
